Regulation (EC) No 32/2000 is amended as follows:
1. In Annex I, for serial number 09.0048, in the second column, CN code " ex 0304 20 95 " is replaced by " ex 0304 20 94 ".
2. Annex IV is amended as follows:
(a) the codes for serial number 09.0104 are amended as follows:
(i) the codes " 4818 20 " to " 4823 90 90 " in the column "CN code" and the text concerning Chapter 48 in the column "Description" are deleted;
(ii) code " ex 9113 90 90 " is replaced by " ex 9113 90 80 ";
(b) for serial number 09.0106, in the column "CN code", code " 6217 17 00 " is replaced by " 6217 10 00 ".
(c) the codes for serial number 09.0104 are amended as follows:
(i) the codes " 4818 20 10 10 " to " 4823 90 90 20 " are deleted;
(ii) in the column "TARIC code", the figure "10" is inserted for CN code " 7117 19 99 ";
(iii) code " 9113 90 90 10 " is replaced by " 9113 90 80 11 ".
